817
01:00:13.077 --> 01:00:18.082
the first cursive script
of ancient Egypt. Way back.

818
01:00:18.749 --> 01:00:21.085
Three thousand years
before Jesus showed up.

819
01:00:21.618 --> 01:00:22.687
